{"tid":2008334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國助台灣藍營、韓國瑜賄選案 國台辦跳腳否認","createTime":"2020-05-09T03:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T06:24:46.000Z","uid":337052,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bc1ebf2707dc44302e13b004e51c1046c65a97b8","tid":2008334,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:26:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中國助藍營、韓國瑜賄選案 國台辦跳腳否認</span></strong><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AXjQjPL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAXjQjPL.jpg&h=6b71c2a3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n中國湖南省台辦等單位去年底涉嫌提供台商資金，並資助機票要求拉抬國民黨總統候選人韓國瑜選情，台北地檢署昨起訴長沙台協會長林懷等7人，中國國台辦發言人馬曉光今天表示，「民進黨當局的所作所為毫不奇怪，實質是破壞兩岸關係，危害台胞利益，製造綠色恐怖」。（中央社資料照）<br />\n<br />\n2020-05-09 10:55:44<br />\n〔記者鍾麗華／台北報導〕中國湖南省台辦等單位去年底涉嫌提供台商資金，並資助機票要求拉抬國民黨總統候選人韓國瑜選情，台北地檢署昨起訴長沙台協會長林懷等7人，中國國台辦發言人馬曉光今天表示，「<strong>民進黨當局的所作所為毫不奇怪，實質是破壞兩岸關係，危害台胞利益，製造『綠色恐怖』</strong>」。<br />\n<br />\n馬曉光說，「近一段時間以來，民進黨當局的卑劣行徑不斷升級，他們為謀求一黨之私，編造各種罪名處罰在大陸的台商台胞，以各種無端藉口打壓，參與兩岸交流合作的台灣團體和人士。只要所持立場與民進黨當局不同，就會受到鋪天蓋地的打壓，製造『綠色恐怖』，引起台灣民眾人人自危。」<br />\n<br />\n台北地檢署調查中國介入台灣選舉案，首次掌握中國替國民黨及其總統候選人韓國瑜賄選的「函文」，幕後金主為中國湖南省長沙市台辦經濟處處長黃道年，以辦餐敘招待食宿及機票等手法，動員台人返台投票給韓國瑜，國民黨陸工會主任周繼祥也被錄到上台致詞；昨<strong>依最重均可處十年徒刑的總統副總統選舉罷免法第86條、公職人員選舉罷免法第99條的賄選罪，起訴林懷等7名台商</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n檢方查出，去年12月11日下午4點30分，長沙台協會在長沙市「華天大酒店」舉辦「2019年湖南台胞年終尾牙聯誼會暨湖南省台灣同胞返鄉投票大會」，主持人為連上銘，舞台背板有韓國瑜競選口號，約500名有投票權的台灣民眾參與，活動提供食宿，還有現金、頭等艙及經濟艙機票、電器、手機等抽獎獎品，全場齊呼「國民黨、加油！」「韓國瑜、凍蒜！」口號。"},{"pid":"5fe71ce809f8dc885fdcc72c52a63fa5c6d99276","tid":2008334,"uid":38988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:29:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">韓國瑜、凍蒜！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">韓國瑜、凍蒜！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">韓國瑜、凍蒜！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">韓國瑜、凍蒜！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">韓國瑜、凍蒜！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">凍你媽逼</span></span>"},{"pid":"da6be8f523ecd4bab0999fdd563dac136dd22688","tid":2008334,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可憐哪"},{"pid":"edd3d464838950aa560003570c9f83064c3b2629","tid":2008334,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fe71ce809f8dc885fdcc72c52a63fa5c6d99276","tid":2008334,"uid":38988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:29:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">韓國瑜、凍蒜！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">韓國瑜、凍蒜！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">韓國瑜、凍蒜！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">韓國瑜、凍蒜！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">韓國瑜、凍蒜！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">凍你媽逼</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab89cb1e5107d71a5085d2babac609cd3e97b45","tid":2008334,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a0ef78d73c0dc34686fd4c3c4ae07d3253d5eb","tid":2008334,"uid":109780,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"da6be8f523ecd4bab0999fdd563dac136dd22688","tid":2008334,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可憐哪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ByYUMAc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FByYUMAc.gif&h=f5285d57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6756e92775399e38265c605351b3dd96c630c16","tid":2008334,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ac5ccb28818205bbfa1d944e7c39f0098be455e","tid":2008334,"uid":46966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:01:31.000Z","msg":"一段時間以來，民進黨當局的卑劣行徑不斷升級，他們為謀求一黨之私，編造各種罪名處罰在大陸的台商台胞，以各種無端藉口打壓，參與兩岸交流合作的台灣團體和人士。只要所持立場與民進黨當局不同，就會受到鋪天蓋地的打壓，製造『綠色恐怖』，引起台灣民眾人人自危。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚好笑喎屌你老味"},{"pid":"9133787487042f39160cf3fa6f175ec5027fd449","tid":2008334,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:09:47.000Z","msg":"光復高雄罷韓黃絲帶發放 600條15分鐘搶光<br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZsiBfEy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZsiBfEy.jpg&h=6780fbe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肉豆公市場發放罷韓黃絲帶。（記者蔡清華攝）<br />\n<br />\n2020-05-09 11:44:05<br />\n〔記者蔡清華／高雄報導〕光復高雄罷韓總部今天上午在鳳山肉豆公市場準備600條黃絲帶發放，吸引民眾排隊索取，一人限拿一條，於15分鐘搶光，民進黨立委許智傑也到場聲援，呼籲市長韓國瑜應讓罷韓選務順利完成，由高雄市民共同來決定他的去留。<br />\n<br />\n今天上午9時， Wecare尹立、張博洋等人到鳳山區肉豆公市場發放黃絲帶，一早就吸引民眾大排長龍等待領取，隊伍長達上百公尺。<br />\n<br />\n張博洋說，昨晚在市府行政中心人行道，強力水柱罷韓印記，今早就被市府人員快速清除，再度展現高效率，他呼籲韓國瑜請勇敢面對罷韓行動，而不是不斷以市府機器阻擋罷韓的聲浪。<br />\n<br />\n尹立說，市府動用公權力高效率的拆除行動，幾乎斬斷罷韓宣傳，今將展開百大路口發放黃絲帶採取化整為零，人人一條黃絲帶傳達市民罷韓決心。<br />\n<br />\n到場聲援的立委許智傑說，市府用一些手段阻撓罷韓投票，只會讓市民更加反感，呼籲市長韓國瑜應讓罷韓選務順利完成，由高雄市民共同來決定他的去留。"},{"pid":"350c957f59dd3e42519cb7bedacdd1f8ab671043","tid":2008334,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ac5ccb28818205bbfa1d944e7c39f0098be455e","tid":2008334,"uid":46966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:01:31.000Z","msg":"一段時間以來，民進黨當局的卑劣行徑不斷升級，他們為謀求一黨之私，編造各種罪名處罰在大陸的台商台胞，以各種無端藉口打壓，參與兩岸交流合作的台灣團體和人士。只要所持立場與民進黨當局不同，就會受到鋪天蓋地的打壓，製造『綠色恐怖』，引起台灣民眾人人自危。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚好笑喎屌你老味"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"啲文筆好似啲獻世派講黑暴 黃色經濟圈乜乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc808ebef554b803c98f4f63b4ef118107f9a21","tid":2008334,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"350c957f59dd3e42519cb7bedacdd1f8ab671043","tid":2008334,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ac5ccb28818205bbfa1d944e7c39f0098be455e","tid":2008334,"uid":46966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:01:31.000Z","msg":"一段時間以來，民進黨當局的卑劣行徑不斷升級，他們為謀求一黨之私，編造各種罪名處罰在大陸的台商台胞，以各種無端藉口打壓，參與兩岸交流合作的台灣團體和人士。只要所持立場與民進黨當局不同，就會受到鋪天蓋地的打壓，製造『綠色恐怖』，引起台灣民眾人人自危。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚好笑喎屌你老味"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"啲文筆好似啲獻世派講黑暴 黃色經濟圈乜乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=